com.sudicode.fb2gh.migrate

Class GHAttachmentUploader

  • Object
    • GHAttachmentUploader
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FBAttachmentConverter, Closeable, AutoCloseable

    public class GHAttachmentUploader
extends Object
implements FBAttachmentConverter, Closeable

    Uploads FogBugz attachments to GitHub Issues. Since the GitHub API does not currently support this, Selenium WebDriver is used instead. This implementation is therefore unstable and should be handled as such. But if it works for you, the more power to you.

    See Also:
    File attachments on issues and pull requests

      • convert

        public String convert(FogBugz fogBugz,
                      FBAttachment fbAttachment)
        Download the FogBugz attachment, then reupload it to GitHub Issues. If the file type is incompatible with GitHub Issues, zip it beforehand. Since ZIP files are supported by GitHub Issues, this guarantees that any attachment (within size constraints) will be accepted.
